name: EXPERT_MONEY
description: Expert Token will function as Youtube Community Token. Rewarding YouTube subscribers will be a mechanism to establish stronger bonds with participants and reward them. The project will evolve into airdrop rewards, staking rewards and participant rewards in the future. Expert Token will be the Token of Real Experts and will distinguish itself in the Solana network. It is the first community token of one of the largest crypto YouTube channels in the world.
